    "description": "Simple, hearty, and warm: A big pot of chili makes for a satisfying dinner any night of the week. Enjoy this on its own or serve it as a plant-based entrée at a casual party. You can also add toppings like guacamole, diced onions, and roasted corn. This will become a staple in your healthy cooking repertoire.",
